rows.label: qst200318_msg0002
rows.name:
How did it go? Ha! Like
I even have to ask!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0005
rows.name:
That Blade and Drivers I told
you about killed the Gogol!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0007
rows.name:
Whoa! It'll be smooth
diggin' from here on in!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0008
rows.name:
No more being afraid of the Gogol
coming for me when I sleep!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0009
rows.name:
Excellent! Excellent!
You are my hero, lad!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0014
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]Gogol is not dead. It roams free.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0017
rows.name:
How could you! What if
it comes back for us?!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0020
rows.name:
You people... You threaten
the Gogols' home.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0022
rows.name:
Violence solves nothing.
I scolded the Gogols.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0023
rows.name: But destroying habitat is your fault.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0027
rows.name: The Gogol who protects family is.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0029
rows.name: You must live in peace with the Gogols.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0030
rows.name: Please. No more robbing Gogols' home!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0036
rows.name:
We'll make sure to stop digging
there. I'll convince our management!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0038
rows.name:
Yeah. After that speech, we can't
just very well do nothing, right?

rows.label: qst200318_msg0039
rows.name:
I mean, we'd get pretty mad if someone
started tearing up our homes!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0040
rows.name:
Treat the Gogols as you'd have
them treat you, that's all.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0042
rows.name:
Sure, no issues here. We
heard you, loud and clear.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0044
rows.name:
You didn't just save us,
but the Gogols, too.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0045
rows.name: I think you are a hero, after all!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0047
rows.name:
Good going, Jikarao! Looks like
you got through to everyone!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0048
rows.name:
Awesome, Jikarao! Looks
like everyone listened!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0049
rows.name:
Well done, Jikarao. It seems
your words have been heard.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0050
rows.name:
Sweet, Jikarao! Seems
people listen to you now!
